# implementation_plan.md

## Goal Description
Modify the "Image Management" (圖片管理) creation interface to improve user experience and clarity.
1. Update terminology: "公告類型" -> "圖片類型", "公告標題" -> "圖片標題".
2. Change the input for "圖片類型" from a radio group to a dropdown menu (Select).

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> The labels "公告類型" and "公告標題" are currently shared with the Announcement system. I will create new translation keys specifically for Image Management to avoid affecting other modules.

